name: Lucky Moon
description:
♥ Merry Christmas 2021 & Happy New Year 2022 ♥

This is Free Edition for thanking community that support me so much. I received many of encouragements, supporting and loves, You know? All of kindness are so precious and cheering me up in the hard time. I don't have enough words to explain how I feel so grateful and appreciated you. Thank for warm welcome to my NFT world. Hope next year we still walk together ♥ Wish you have your best year in 2022!
